title: No One Saw that TWIST Coming! #ad (Citadel on Prime) #shorts
description:
👀 Watch the Citadel finale on @PrimeVideo this Friday!

As if this season of Citadel hasn’t been CRAZY enough, this was a bizarre twist that no one saw coming: Mason and Nadia have a secret baby! WHAT?! Everything is finally making sense. Nadia is no longer a suspect of being a double agent, but Abby and Mason are both prime candidates. So what will happen in the FINALE of Citadel on Prime this Friday? Let us know in the comments.
